

# Title: summary, imperative           50 chars=>#           72 chars=>#
# * <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# * type:
#   * chore: Build process or auxiliary tool changes
#   * ci: CI related changes
#   * docs: Documentation only changes
#   * feat: A new feature
#   * fix: A bug fix
#   * perf: A code change that improves performance
#   * refactor: A code change with no bugfix or new feature added
#   * style: Markup, white-space, formatting, missing semi-colons
#   * test: Adding missing tests
# * scope: component or file name

# <body>: explain *WHAT* and *WHY* (not *HOW*) =========================
# * What problem is being solved?
# * What is the solution to said problem?
# * Are there any side effects or dependencies?

# <footer>: closing reference or issue link, if any ====================
# * Include at least one empty line before it.
# * Include Co-authored-by for all contributors. Format: 
#   * Co-authored-by: name <user@users.noreply.github.com>
#
# ======================================================================
